Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八号机构
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.55,0:02:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎式圆环态  法兰克王国的车轮刑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.55,0:02:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16}{\pos(380,325)}Breaking  by  Wheel  at  Francs
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.33,0:02:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祸动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样  我一直在期待能这样享受一番
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.17,0:02:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  发出令人愉悦的悲鸣然后崩坏吧  贱人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.78,0:02:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起讴歌悲鸣的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.81,0:02:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我相比有着数百年的差距
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.97,0:02:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哀嚎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三号机构  断式落下态
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.56,0:03:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,断头台
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.56,0:03:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16}Guillotine
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.95,0:03:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贱人  贱人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然  居然敢这样玩弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.02,0:03:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贱人  贱人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你杀掉  毁掉  完全破坏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.25,0:04:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.95,0:04:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法兰克王国的车轮刑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祸动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲鸣  我想听别人的悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是为此而被制造的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.43,0:04:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是…如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快恢复过来  已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.69,0:04:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人已经逃走了  菲亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.28,0:04:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.97,0:04:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:04:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.28,0:05:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是第一次见到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.01,0:05:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  原来是如此的冰冷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.15,0:05:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下你明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.45,0:05:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所想要知道的我的本性
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样子的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.49,0:05:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春亮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她所说的话全都是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我杀害了数百人  是为了杀戮而制造的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才被诅咒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而值得讽刺的是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.75,0:05:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于诅咒获得了人的意识
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认识到了「罪」这一概念
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常会有…这种事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.85,0:05:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所背负的诅咒是单纯的那个「常有」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必定会使持有者发狂  令他不得不使用我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.78,0:05:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  这诅咒是常有的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.19,0:06:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了吧  你的诅咒对我无效
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在这里也没任何问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.95,0:06:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.15,0:06:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我察觉到我根本的问题是什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拼命地追寻着愿望  希望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.48,0:06:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也曾想过不去考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.21,0:06:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也曾想过就此忘却
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.65,0:06:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是不可能的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.39,0:06:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲亚  冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有罪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.55,0:06:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人  杀人无数的罪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.06,0:06:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此我背负着被诅咒的罪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.94,0:06:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  惩罚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.36,0:06:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惩罚是…什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  我还能够被救赎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.42,0:06:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家吧  这里实在太冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.53,0:06:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的回答真是温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温柔得令人讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然还是不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  菲亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.75,0:07:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  春亮君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春亮君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.91,0:07:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  菲亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.05,0:07:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还不可以起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然做了些急救措施
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.13,0:07:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是血还是流了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.60,0:07:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  你不是已经帮我避开要害了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.04,0:07:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不会有什么大碍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.81,0:08:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这是命令式的提议
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.24,0:08:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去医院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.82,0:08:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去的话  会如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.18,0:08:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会生气的哦  就算是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.78,0:08:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便找到她又能如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是自愿离开的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.20,0:08:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算失去了一只手也毫无放弃的念头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.12,0:08:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为逃跑也是一种很好的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙当时说一个人沉睡下去更好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.02,0:08:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.39,0:08:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是打算以更糟糕的方式来了结
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.37,0:08:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  这是我一生的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此叶姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.86,0:09:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真卑鄙  不是说好不再这样叫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们都是高中生了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.11,0:09:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前像这样求你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有一次是不答应我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.73,0:09:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是我的自言自语
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.57,0:09:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想她只是没弄懂最浅显易见的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一件非常简单的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.09,0:09:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么一回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.24,0:09:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  我的自言自语被听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.14,0:09:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然被听到  那就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是她的疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.39,0:09:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于罪和诅咒的提示
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.37,0:09:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单来说的话就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.61,0:09:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也还没有从春亮君这里得到回答
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她跟我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.34,0:09:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟以前的我想着同样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.85,0:09:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也与现在的我一样  仍未得到答案
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.04,0:09:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我一直都留在春亮君的家里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.28,0:10:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.90,0:10:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此叶姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.54,0:10:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.73,0:10:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怜的悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.38,0:10:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滑稽的悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凄惨的悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.18,0:10:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的悲鸣听起来都是那么的熟悉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.12,0:10:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为道具的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.93,0:10:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾是道具的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.80,0:10:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被操控  被使用  被需要的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲鸣…悲鸣…悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.45,0:10:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证明着我依然是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.49,0:10:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.91,0:10:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.03,0:10:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲亚君？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.37,0:11:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲亚君  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.91,0:11:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  菲…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.61,0:11:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  悲鸣就够吵的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.54,0:11:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲鸣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.83,0:11:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是十九号机构
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.51,0:11:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抉式螺旋态  人体钻孔机
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.51,0:11:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16}{\pos(380,325)}Man-Perforater
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.11,0:11:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我  这是我的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.07,0:11:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用次数是357次又或是358次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一次使用的时候是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.56,0:11:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是上野锥霞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.33,0:11:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你班上的班长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.01,0:11:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手  菲亚君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.29,0:12:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲亚…君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.07,0:12:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.80,0:12:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物绷带
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.80,0:12:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16}Chupacabran  vantage
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.47,0:12:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开…玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.92,0:12:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.86,0:12:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经喝饱了  应该
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤口…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.60,0:12:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物绷带是活体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.53,0:13:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以吸血的时候会产生剧痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.13,0:13:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治疗致命的创伤  强加致命的疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.25,0:13:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是这个绷带所附带的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.28,0:13:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的后方支援员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.72,0:13:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是性命攸关的事态
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才出手相助
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.70,0:13:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.79,0:13:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么自作主张
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.54,0:13:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还能战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.87,0:13:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个臭婊子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管多少次都要摧毁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让前卫的骑士能完成使命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.02,0:13:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后方支援员要提供最大的支援
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.73,0:13:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我确信  我的判断是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.00,0:13:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你无谓地丧命  我也会被认为无能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.88,0:13:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么样的后方支援员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱掉披着的头巾  让我看看你的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是必要的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.63,0:14:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋  跑到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.66,0:14:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到菲亚君了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在哪里  我现在在找她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.47,0:14:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看她的样子很奇怪就叫住了她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.38,0:14:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  没发生什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在那家伙情绪有点不安定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许  什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.81,0:14:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.24,0:14:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.01,0:14:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是  要怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.64,0:14:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话  我有点混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.89,0:14:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到不可思议的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.22,0:14:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲亚君她  菲亚君她拿着的那个魔方…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.78,0:14:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班长  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:14:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能先忘掉这件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.15,0:14:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.14,0:15:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等安定下来后一定会给你解释的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.37,0:15:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像也有难言之隐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.48,0:15:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.44,0:15:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  班长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为我存在的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.17,0:15:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地上沾满的血
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水沟流淌的血
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.89,0:15:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,染红河水的血
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.63,0:15:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  为我清洗血迹的某人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.65,0:15:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擦拭血迹  为我准备新血的某人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但  我喜欢过他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.75,0:15:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为只有他对我说过话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.61,0:15:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我说过同情的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.81,0:15:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到现在我都还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.55,0:15:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得他的悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.60,0:15:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得曾经喜欢过的  他的悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.12,0:15:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我强迫他发出的悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:16:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次看到的大海…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何让我想起了以前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以作为初次的结束
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也未尝不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.36,0:16:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.84,0:16:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得想想看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是什么样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.44,0:16:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想想看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.78,0:16:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  比电视里看到的还要阴森
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.36,0:16:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  一片漆黑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.01,0:16:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无尽的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.83,0:16:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是我以前待过的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.21,0:16:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却又为何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.26,0:16:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此难舍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  何必这样难舍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.19,0:17:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才还试图杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不可能来追我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被诅咒的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.65,0:17:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我被诅咒着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.68,0:17:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冰  好冷  好黑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.05,0:17:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是回到本属于我的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  远比以前要寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记关键的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.19,0:18:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙很重  而且还很傻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.07,0:18:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以跳海也不会想个好位置
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我就去一趟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.68,0:18:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.65,0:18:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.80,0:18:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.34,0:18:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  是那么回事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和本体一个样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.51,0:18:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超重的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.74,0:18:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说我重  已经是第二次了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.99,0:18:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次是什么时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.23,0:18:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你刚被寄来的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.35,0:18:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然对一个淑女说这样的粗话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.91,0:18:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诅…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰巧啊  我也在气头上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.45,0:18:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诅咒你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.58,0:18:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.88,0:18:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说一次  诅咒你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.99,0:18:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的诅咒很厉害的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.56,0:18:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  不想被我诅咒的话就别说话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.68,0:19:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放我下来  别管我  什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.87,0:19:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要敢说的话就会被诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.81,0:19:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会怎样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.63,0:19:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸部再也长不大了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.48,0:19:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来我就不会受你诅咒的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的  没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.60,0:19:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用  所以你威胁我我也不会觉得怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.44,0:19:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不会听你任性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.93,0:19:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不会让你自作主张地离家出走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你走几次都要把你拉回来  做好觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.15,0:19:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真嚣张  明明是不知羞耻的小毛孩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可真对不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.31,0:19:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样听我说一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.99,0:19:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.83,0:19:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.72,0:19:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不趁现在说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.90,0:19:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怕以后会不敢说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.13,0:19:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.42,0:19:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很害怕别人的悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.53,0:19:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确地说是害怕亲近的人的悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.44,0:20:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像今天这样  你被人伤害而惨叫的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又会变成原来的我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.03,0:20:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要甩掉我的话  就趁现在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.34,0:20:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.11,0:20:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂我有没有资格留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不懂我有没有资格消除我的诅咒和罪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.21,0:20:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.06,0:20:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不记得我有说过需要什么资格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.46,0:20:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想待在这里就待着咯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是  你想不想待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.60,0:20:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为你不受诅咒就可以小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.70,0:20:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有更直接的诅咒方法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样  很冰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.95,0:20:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你还嚣张
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你受感冒的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.47,0:20:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可真的恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.21,0:20:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是谁  每年都会受到一次的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.50,0:22:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等下  菲亚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.06,0:22:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  给我老实点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.83,0:22:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要为你擦背
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.41,0:22:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.78,0:22:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别脱我衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.50,0:22:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真会感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.05,0:22:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能脱裤子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.37,0:22:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.18,0:22:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上野同学她担心你  好不容易来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.57,0:22:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.80,0:22:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.54,0:22:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是个误会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.84,0:22:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么误会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.31,0:23:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实我是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.54,0:23:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能没法满足你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.27,0:23:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会努力用我的身体侍奉你让你舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.71,0:23:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再放过你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.72,0:23:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要跟你一起住
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.03,0:23:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四章  晚上需要妈妈和抱枕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.95,0:23:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不看的话诅咒你哦


